Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都说我骨折了还过来面试\N非常的认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-能当正职就太好了\N-一起去车站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说了不能在墙上订东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这也要找你们要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-那里不用吧-那是卧室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,房间就不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等下-关系不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么-没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子是很早之前做的\N墙壁都很薄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的情侣每天都做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们很老实很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,叫的时候也很克制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我拜托人把东西都弄走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的都愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们在这里再呆一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我打扫卫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,最近我的腰不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老婆又没有了 现在靠房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给我打扫卫生和做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你又没工作\N男朋友身体又是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该是好提案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-应该可以做到吧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,时间可以自我安排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很讨厌的样子\N人还不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 虽然总是高高在上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天面试也不行了\N拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-不好意思\N-没事吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,开动了-开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起-我先洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那里等你去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:08:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,外面是当家政妇\N但其实这是当爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不会告诉你男友的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你那男友很烂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌吗 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再来再来-住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,知道该怎么做吧-住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧-住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很久没做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他的肉棒不行了吧\N-快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只是摸一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他插进去之后马上\N就会射了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这么下流的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-大家都一样\N-跟房东有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就付房租
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,身体太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我一下就射了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌-手拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都到这个程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来让你爽-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿开来弄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,男友能让你爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮-来看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了-想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,说谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说来吃-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌-这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-乳头硬了怎么了\N放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,说讨厌 但是很爽对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,适可而止-不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这个这样怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌不要这样弄\N-这样比较爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这个比摸爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌-这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-讨厌-好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌-就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手别弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行还没玩够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了屁股太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了好味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,过来-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N-做这样的事会被别人发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样好吗\N发出声音也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的房间和别的房间比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,隔音好很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吃-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样来就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来让我吃手拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌-手拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,住手讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧-住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧直接来吃-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-手吗-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃手-讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么出来了-住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好甜好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌-不行来吃来吃
