Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没有-很爽吧这样
