Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:23:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.58,0:24:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
