Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.70,0:51:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.01,0:51:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那再来弄快点
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.61,0:51:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想要真肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.68,0:51:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.35,0:51:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来 好东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.63,0:51:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 来屁股摇动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.67,0:51:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.34,0:51:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样来吃来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.38,0:51:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.62,0:51:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.15,0:52:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这周围都要认真吃
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.79,0:52:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的用力
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.36,0:52:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.07,0:52:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,跟之前说的要吃深些
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.94,0:52:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当你的嘴巴是小穴-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.75,0:52:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么小穴怎么弄爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.52,0:52:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来弄爽些
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.87,0:52:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你男友不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.94,0:52:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 是的 .是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.18,0:53:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,碍事的全部都脱了-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.85,0:53:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.92,0:53:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.03,0:53:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.21,0:53:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.05,0:53:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.02,0:53:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.33,0:53:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.00,0:53:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.03,0:53:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想要就这样吃
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.17,0:54:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗-是的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.65,0:54:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.12,0:54:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头很硬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.86,0:54:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样弄
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.36,0:54:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.00,0:54:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-再来吃-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.72,0:54:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吃
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.04,0:55:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.94,0:55:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.75,0:55:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.98,0:55:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.52,0:55:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.39,0:55:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 表情真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.47,0:55:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样 都是唾液吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.31,0:55:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,满了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.01,0:55:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要放开
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.11,0:55:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在松开 都吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.58,0:55:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 就这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.92,0:55:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,用手来动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.46,0:55:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.66,0:56:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,旁边也是一边吃\N一边用手来弄
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.17,0:56:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.07,0:56:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.28,0:56:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.90,0:56:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.66,0:57:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 就这样来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.44,0:57:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开 嘴巴小穴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.86,0:57:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,像小穴那样来弄
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.30,0:57:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.53,0:57:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.27,0:57:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就射在嘴巴里-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.84,0:57:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就射在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.52,0:58:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.99,0:58:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.99,0:58:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.76,0:58:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,手放上来好好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.07,0:58:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用力
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.14,0:58:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吃
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.28,0:58:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.55,0:58:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.03,0:58:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再来认真吃
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.53,0:58:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的就这样吃
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.68,0:59:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.24,0:59:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.85,0:59:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.12,0:59:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴小穴都塞满了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.37,1:00:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只是嘴巴还不满足吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.14,1:00:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.15,1:00:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.09,1:00:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,弄好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.28,1:00:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.95,1:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧-是的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.62,1:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来给你吃
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.70,1:01:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.57,1:01:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想要插小穴吧自己弄出来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.45,1:01:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的味道
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.89,1:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样来想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.60,1:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.33,1:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,说绐我肉棒-绐我肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.84,1:01:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.88,1:01:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.32,1:01:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.72,1:02:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了-要高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.36,1:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.01,1:02:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,接着再来-好的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.14,1:02:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.55,1:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.07,1:02:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.56,1:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好的味道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.13,1:03:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要吗-好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.63,1:03:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.34,1:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.38,1:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了要高潮了高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.93,1:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,做你男友不给你做的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.20,1:03:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你男友这样弄吗 接下来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.34,1:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等下要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.39,1:04:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一好爽不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.62,1:04:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽-不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.02,1:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.03,1:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行里面要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.08,1:04:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.52,1:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒都插进去了再说
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.96,1:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.37,1:05:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.58,1:05:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.15,1:05:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.96,1:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.87,1:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.15,1:05:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.15,1:05:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.50,1:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.20,1:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行要高潮了高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.12,1:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.07,1:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,手放后面来分开
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.62,1:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.32,1:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,里面这样插好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.83,1:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱这样插可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.77,1:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.57,1:07:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么-肉棒在插
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.84,1:07:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,狠狠的插更爽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.42,1:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了好下流
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.76,1:07:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.63,1:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,里面受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.80,1:07:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.90,1:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-里面要高潮了\N想不想高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.38,1:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-想吗-让我来高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.59,1:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.43,1:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.76,1:08:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样-好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.31,1:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,狠狠的插里面-这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.11,1:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.84,1:10:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.65,1:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要狠狠的插吗是的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.32,1:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.59,1:10:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.59,1:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.06,1:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.90,1:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-好爽不行要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.70,1:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,—起射吧-高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.11,1:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.75,1:11:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.22,1:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,刚房产中介来电话了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.49,1:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你男友过来面试\N看到地址才知道
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.13,1:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是很好的房产中介
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.91,1:11:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就让他进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.11,1:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我们说
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.45,1:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有经验 可是有野心\N所以拜托我们了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.39,1:12:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要三个人祝贺他才行
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.70,1:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-好酒-来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.84,1:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样-已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.98,1:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开始家政妇打工结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.49,1:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,来祝贺你男友找到工作
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.73,1:12:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧干杯-干杯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.00,1:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我做饭很好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.74,1:12:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我去弄吧-好的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.55,1:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧-没事没事
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.08,1:13:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小心-好的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.49,1:13:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不说-做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.36,1:13:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.10,1:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我全部都说了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.50,1:13:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗-我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.84,1:13:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,过来过来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.91,1:13:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.28,1:13:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来弄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.08,1:13:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,会看见的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.62,1:13:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快点来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.23,1:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤脱了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.50,1:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.90,1:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.92,1:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这样来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.99,1:14:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.77,1:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不穿内裤自慰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.14,1:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.65,1:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢变态
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.42,1:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.62,1:14:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,弄下流点
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.33,1:14:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再翘起来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.50,1:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再来-是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.97,1:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个笨蛋女人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.31,1:15:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,过来让我来弄-不行
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.12,1:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别弄了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.01,1:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要忍住
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.46,1:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-房东 酱油在哪
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.59,1:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是放在上面棚子了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.03,1:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要客气 用吧\N真的是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.57,1:16:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.24,1:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,冰箱里的东西随便用
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.65,1:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.95,1:16:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来来看
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.29,1:16:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.23,1:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,忍着吧 变熊女人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.24,1:16:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,过来倒酒
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.58,1:16:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.05,1:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,倒出来了出来了-受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.09,1:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要弄那么快
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.60,1:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.73,1:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.20,1:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,里面受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.67,1:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再来弄快些
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.74,1:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快点结束吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.88,1:17:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.23,1:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.69,1:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 要高潮了高潮了
